## 📋 Final Test Summary

This comprehensive test covers:
- ✅ All Element types (10+ components)
- ✅ All Collection types (6+ components) 
- ✅ All View types (5+ components)
- ✅ All Module types (6+ components)
- ✅ Component states and variations
- ✅ Nested and complex layouts
- ✅ Edge cases and special characters
- ✅ Responsive design features

Total components tested: 30+ with multiple variations each.

